profile: Lejan Land Surveying Inc is a privately owned company licensed and operated under a Certificate of Authorization issued by the Association of Ontario Land Surveyors. Through our extensive surveying experience and using the latest most efficient equipment we provide our customers with reliable deliverables on time, every time. We offer property boundary surveys, reference plans, topographic surveys to facilitate site plans, and also precise monitoring of structures. Visit us at www.lejansurveying.ca
